Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.19,0:01:30.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:89193,90528}I'm leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.52,0:01:31.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:90528,91946}Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.32,0:01:34.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:93323,94407}Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.24,0:01:40.66,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:99245,100663}Thank you, Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.66,0:01:45.66,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:100663,105668}You thought I forgot my bag and I was on\Nmy way to school, so you brought it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.66,0:01:48.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:105668,108296}But I don't need a bag!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.67,0:01:51.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:108671,111674}Today we will go for a stroll outside the city!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.67,0:01:54.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:111674,114510}Look, this is for lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.80,0:01:58.34,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:114802,118348}So I don't want you to go to school today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.60,0:02:07.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:125605,127440}Do you want to go too?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.73,0:02:14.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:132737,134489}Everyone is ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.48,0:02:15.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:134489,135698}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.24,0:02:18.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:136240,138951}You understand, Lassie?\NYou have to wait until we move.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.95,0:02:20.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:138951,140703}What will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.99,0:02:23.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:141996,143206}Hello John!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.20,0:02:25.45,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:143206,145458}Will Lassie be released today?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.45,0:02:26.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:145458,146793}Yes that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.16,0:02:29.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:147168,149295}Because they went to the cart regularly!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.67,0:02:31.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:149671,151297}- Yes!\N- Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.83,0:02:33.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:151839,153925}You seem to have difficulty in your youth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.92,0:02:37.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:153925,157804}The teacher ended up going in a school trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.80,0:02:39.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:157804,159847}But I am very excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.93,0:02:44.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:161933,164560}Everything is okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.10,0:02:48.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:167105,168064}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.10,0:02:52.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:170108,172235}Everyone, we will move now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.23,0:02:55.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:172235,175571}Take care not to fall from the cart!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.57,0:02:56.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:175571,176572}- Yes!\N- Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.98,0:02:59.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:176989,179409}- Now, please!\N- Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.04,0:03:08.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:186040,188209}Come on! Come! Come!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.79,0:03:13.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:191796,193172}In here! In here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.97,0:03:22.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:200972,202223}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.43,0:03:26.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:204434,206227}Nothing at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.00,0:03:58.34,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:235006,238342}All of you, get off of the cart\Nand then board on the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.34,0:04:00.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:238342,240470}I go first to the reception!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.47,0:04:01.76,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:240470,241763}We'll go get the tickets!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.26,0:04:04.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:243264,244307}Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.30,0:04:05.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:244307,245808}Come on! Move! Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.80,0:04:06.76,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:245808,246768}Y-yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.64,0:04:11.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:250646,251856}Uncle, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.85,0:04:13.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:251856,253107}We depend on you to return!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.10,0:04:15.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:253107,255985}Yes, be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.82,0:04:20.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:258821,260156}No, Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.57,0:04:22.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:261574,262408}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.55,0:04:51.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:288559,291312}We are on board now, but what next?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.31,0:04:54.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:291312,294315}Where can I hide Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.31,0:04:56.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:294315,296359}John, it's the teacher Curry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.35,0:04:57.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:296359,297235}Uh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.23,0:04:59.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:297235,299237}Colin, I rely on you to take care of Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.23,0:05:02.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:301239,302532}Teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.53,0:05:04.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:302532,304617}What's the matter, John Carraclough?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.61,0:05:06.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:304617,306577}Sorry, this…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.53,0:05:09.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:307537,309205}I have a question!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.20,0:05:09.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:309205,309872}Uh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.54,0:05:13.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:310540,313125}I must hide Lassie…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.05,0:05:26.55,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:325054,326556}This is bad…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.56,0:05:34.81,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:333563,334814}Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.56,0:05:41.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:339569,341404}Thank you, dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.40,0:05:42.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:341404,342738}That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.73,0:05:44.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:342738,344365}Hey!  You are…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.99,0:05:48.16,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:346993,348160}My hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.03,0:05:53.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:351038,353875}Damn, it was my hat that I loved!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.87,0:05:55.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:353875,355918}Sorry…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.50,0:06:01.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:359505,361549}We can't recover it anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.54,0:06:03.00,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:361549,363009}I will forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.59,0:06:09.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:367597,369807}Right, I have to hide Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.80,0:06:11.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:369807,371142}- Hide?\N- Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.35,0:06:13.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:372351,373936}I know a good place!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.93,0:06:14.81,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:373936,374812}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.56,0:06:19.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:375563,379233}I see! I'm also going to the same place, Skull Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.23,0:06:21.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:379233,381152}T-t-the same place?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.15,0:06:27.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:381152,387992}Yep. But when we return I'll go to a different\Nship, which is bound for Australia.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.99,0:06:30.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:387992,390828}My father went before me\Nand now he is waiting for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.41,0:06:32.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:391412,392872}You are a foreigner…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.87,0:06:35.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:392872,395291}I wanted to see one of you already…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.54,0:06:42.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:400546,402089}Tell me, what is the name?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.08,0:06:43.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:402089,403174}It's Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.17,0:06:45.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:403174,405259}Wrong, I mean your name!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.25,0:06:46.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:405259,406052}Uh…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.05,0:06:46.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:406052,406802}Uh… eh…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.80,0:06:47.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:406802,407845}Co-Colin…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.22,0:06:49.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:408220,409639}I'm Chris!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.63,0:06:50.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:409639,410848}Nice to meet you, Colin!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.39,0:06:53.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:412391,413851}Nice to meet you, Chris!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.43,0:06:56.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:414435,416145}Nice to meet you, Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.52,0:07:01.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:419523,421359}- Uh… uh…\N- Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.94,0:07:04.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:421943,424695}A-a little while ago… What was that paper?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.69,0:07:06.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:424695,426864}It seemed important.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.86,0:07:09.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:426864,429992}That's it! A treasure map!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.99,0:07:11.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:429992,431077}A treasure map?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.87,0:07:20.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:435873,440920}When I get to Skull Island\NI'll look for a treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.92,0:07:22.71,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:440920,442713}C-can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.71,0:07:23.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:442713,443255}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.25,0:07:26.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:443255,446676}Y-you can consider that instead\Nof the hat you lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.67,0:07:28.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:446676,448844}Lassie, do you want to go with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.47,0:07:40.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:458479,460064}Colin Jones?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.94,0:07:43.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:460940,463776}Does anyone know where Colin Jones is?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.36,0:07:47.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:464360,467530}Maybe we should search the ship again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.53,0:07:48.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:467530,468447}It's bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.44,0:07:49.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:468447,469865}He can't get out just like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.86,0:07:52.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:469865,472034}This is because he's alone with with Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.03,0:07:53.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:472034,473035}Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.03,0:07:55.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:473035,475579}Could it have fallen into the sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.57,0:07:56.78,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:475579,476789}Oh…!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.41,0:07:58.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:477415,478791}Oh…!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.37,0:08:01.50,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:479375,481502}Colin! Las--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.50,0:08:04.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:481502,484338}You brought Lassie with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.33,0:08:06.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:484338,486173}No, I mean…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.17,0:08:07.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:486173,487842}Teacher, I have a question!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.84,0:08:09.55,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:487842,489552}I will answer later!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.42,0:08:12.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:490428,492596}Teacher, I apologize for the delay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.59,0:08:14.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:492596,494056}Colin, what about the dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.22,0:08:17.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:495224,497351}What do you want from Sebastian?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.35,0:08:18.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:497351,498561}Sebastian?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.56,0:08:20.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:498561,500062}Is this dog's name?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.39,0:08:21.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:500396,501605}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.60,0:08:24.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:501605,504316}Say "Hello", Sebastian!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.02,0:08:27.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:506027,507194}What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.19,0:08:28.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:507194,508154}I'm Chris!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.15,0:08:30.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:508154,510239}We have become friends on the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.23,0:08:32.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:510239,512533}Well, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.53,0:08:36.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:512533,516328}Now get ready, we will eat\Nour lunch in the lighthouse!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.32,0:08:37.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:516328,517913}Now, let's move!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.91,0:08:38.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:517913,518873}- Yes!\N- Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.95,0:08:42.71,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:520958,522710}What does that mean, Colin?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.87,0:08:46.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:523878,526172}Hello John! Sandy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.17,0:08:46.71,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:526172,526714}- Hm?\N- Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.13,0:08:49.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:527131,529175}I'm Chris, nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.17,0:08:51.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:529175,531427}Colin told me about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.42,0:08:53.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:531427,533721}It was a good plan, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.72,0:08:54.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:533721,534680}Ah…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.68,0:08:56.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:534680,536390}Hello, Chris!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.39,0:09:00.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:536390,540603}When we have a vacuum, you need\Nto take care of the Lassie thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.60,0:09:01.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:540603,541228}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.22,0:09:02.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:541228,542521}That would be a good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.98,0:09:05.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:542980,545024}I will wait for you in that place!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.27,0:09:06.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:545274,546025}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.02,0:09:07.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:546025,547568}I rely on you to take care of Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.56,0:09:09.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:547568,549528}Let's go, Sebastian!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.65,0:09:11.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:550654,551530}Ah, a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.49,0:09:14.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:552490,554241}This…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.24,0:09:15.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:554241,555743}It's Lassie's lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.28,0:09:17.49,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:556285,557495}I understand, see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.49,0:09:19.49,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:557495,559497}We'll meet later!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.08,0:09:21.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:560081,561957}- Farewell, Chris!\N- No… But…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.95,0:09:22.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:561957,562750}As I thougt!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.08,0:09:25.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:563084,565252}Hey Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.58,0:09:32.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:568589,572968}When it heard its name it didn't turn back.\NMaybe it's really another dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.96,0:09:33.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:572968,573886}- Ah…\N- Ah…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.43,0:09:41.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:579433,581477}It's nice to listen to the sea, Robert!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.76,0:09:43.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:581769,583020}I want to go too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.02,0:09:43.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:583020,583938}Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.93,0:09:46.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:583938,586482}Treasure hunt… This is very exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.27,0:09:48.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:587274,588984}Is it on that island?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.98,0:09:51.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:588984,591487}It's an island but we can walk on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.48,0:09:52.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:591487,592905}Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.90,0:09:54.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:592905,594907}In leisure time to look for treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.90,0:09:56.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:594907,596617}Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.61,0:09:57.49,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:596617,597493}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.49,0:09:58.49,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:597493,598494}Colin?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.74,0:09:59.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:598744,599954}Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.95,0:10:03.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:599954,603916}You can go down to the white sandy beach\Nin the afternoon when it's warm!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.91,0:10:05.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:603916,605793}Don't go far away!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.79,0:10:08.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:605793,608963}Also don't go on that island!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.42,0:10:10.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:609421,610131}You understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.13,0:10:11.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:610131,611298}- Yes!\N- Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.92,0:10:13.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:611924,613968}We can't go to the island…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.96,0:10:15.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:613968,615261}I wonder why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.56,0:10:24.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:623561,624270}Were you waiting?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.27,0:10:25.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:624270,625312}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.31,0:10:27.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:625312,627898}- And this will restore Lassie to you!\N- Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.31,0:10:29.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:628315,629567}John!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.56,0:10:31.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:629567,631902}I have to go with Chris.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.73,0:10:33.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:632736,633904}But the teacher said…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.57,0:10:36.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:634572,636949}Colin, I don't want to force you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.94,0:10:38.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:636949,638117}I can go by myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.11,0:10:39.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:638117,639410}No, it's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.91,0:10:41.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:639910,641912}I want to go…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.62,0:10:43.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:642621,643831}A-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.83,0:10:45.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:643831,645374}Is that so, Colin?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.83,0:10:47.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:645833,647126}I will go too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.12,0:10:48.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:647126,648043}You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.04,0:10:49.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:648043,649587}Ah, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.58,0:10:50.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:649587,650921}It's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.92,0:10:52.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:650921,652882}Colin, you can go on your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.04,0:10:55.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:654049,655134}Alone…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.63,0:11:00.38,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:656635,660389}Sorry, I wanted to take Lassie with us but…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.51,0:11:02.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:661515,662516}It's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.51,0:11:04.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:662516,664435}W-what is the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.43,0:11:05.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:664435,665561}Sorry, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.56,0:11:07.18,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:665561,667188}Come on, Chris!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.18,0:11:09.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:667188,669940}I'll borrow Lassie again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.94,0:11:11.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:669940,671901}Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.11,0:11:21.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:679116,681869}Lassie follows them too…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.86,0:11:24.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:681869,684371}Listen, why can't I go?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.37,0:11:26.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:684371,686916}John, it's too boring!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.91,0:11:28.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:686916,688209}Boring?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.20,0:11:29.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:688209,689919}I mean…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.16,0:11:31.00,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:690169,691003}Eh…?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.00,0:11:32.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:691003,692421}Love her?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.42,0:11:33.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:692421,693839}What does Colin mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.83,0:11:35.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:693839,695090}That's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.09,0:11:36.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:695090,696425}Eh…?
Comment: 0,0:11:47.89,0:11:47.89,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:707895,707895}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.23,0:11:56.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:714235,716695}Listen, how does the treasure look?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.69,0:12:00.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:716695,720532}Could you have seen two hackers before?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.53,0:12:01.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:720532,721533}Wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.53,0:12:03.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:721533,723244}It's a little trifle!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.24,0:12:05.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:723244,725996}In the eyes of people is worthless!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.99,0:12:08.66,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:725996,728666}But for me it's my precious treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.08,0:12:10.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:729083,730876}Right…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.87,0:12:14.21,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:730876,734213}It isn't a pirate treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.21,0:12:15.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:734213,735172}What do I have?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.17,0:12:16.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:735172,736090}Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.09,0:12:20.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:736090,740177}Not so, but I knew nothing\Nabout the treasure at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.55,0:12:25.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:744556,745474}Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.47,0:12:28.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:745474,748102}Wait! Chris!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.23,0:12:36.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:754233,756735}I want to look for treasure…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.73,0:12:40.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:756735,760739}But Colin…Do you really love Chris?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.73,0:12:42.78,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:760739,762783}I think he doesn't care about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.78,0:12:43.78,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:762783,763784}Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.78,0:12:45.49,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:763784,765494}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.49,0:12:47.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:765494,767037}I was just xxx!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.03,0:12:48.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:767037,768622}John the insensitive!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.62,0:12:49.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:768622,769248}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.24,0:12:51.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:769248,771834}Do you know anything about the age of love?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.83,0:12:54.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:771834,774545}Damn, I'm not insensitive…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.08,0:12:56.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:775087,776422}Just for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.42,0:12:58.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:776422,778549}Boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.43,0:13:05.76,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:784430,785764}We have climbed a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.68,0:13:08.76,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:786682,788767}Chris, is this really the way?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.22,0:13:12.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:789226,792271}Yes, if we walk this way we will\Nreach the top of the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.52,0:13:15.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:793522,795274}Up to the peak…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.69,0:13:20.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:798694,800612}Are you fine? You're tired?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.61,0:13:22.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:800612,802698}I-I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.69,0:13:24.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:802698,804158}That's it…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.36,0:13:28.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:807369,808954}It's pushing hard…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.54,0:13:36.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:814543,816253}John Carraclough!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.92,0:13:39.38,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:817921,819381}John Carraclough!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.38,0:13:41.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:819381,821133}I have a question for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.13,0:13:43.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:821133,823052}Y-yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.85,0:13:51.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:830851,831894}This…?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.89,0:13:53.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:831894,833937}It's a landslide…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.93,0:13:55.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:833937,835439}I don't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.85,0:13:57.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:835856,837941}Although we have had all\Nthe trouble to get here…!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.65,0:14:08.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:846658,848410}Lassie does it perfectly!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.41,0:14:09.66,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:848410,849661}Let's go through there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.66,0:14:12.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:849661,852998}Look, Lassie walks the natural way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.62,0:14:16.16,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:853624,856168}But we can't climb like Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.16,0:14:18.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:856168,858128}Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.12,0:14:20.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:858128,860923}I'll make holes for climbing, with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.92,0:14:21.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:860923,861757}Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.75,0:14:23.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:861757,863842}I'll start digging!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.84,0:14:26.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:863842,866095}So stay away and wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.09,0:14:27.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:866095,867262}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.99,0:14:51.66,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:889993,891662}Now climb up, Chris!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.66,0:14:52.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:891662,892329}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.74,0:14:57.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:895749,897251}Don't look down!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.25,0:15:00.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:897251,900337}Yes, you can fix your feet this way.\NCome on!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.05,0:15:08.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:906051,908303}We have already reached the peak!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.30,0:15:08.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:908303,908971}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.97,0:15:10.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:908971,910139}And now…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.13,0:15:11.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:910139,911723}Listen, show me the map!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.72,0:15:12.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:911723,912641}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.64,0:15:13.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:912641,913475}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.68,0:15:16.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:914685,916019}A compass!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.01,0:15:17.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:916019,917980}It looks like a real treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.98,0:15:21.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:917980,921108}But it doesn't help as long\Nas we don't have a map!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.10,0:15:22.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:921108,922651}Not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.65,0:15:25.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:922651,925195}Thay way is the lighthouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.19,0:15:28.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:925195,928115}So I think the treasure is to the northwest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.07,0:15:32.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:931076,932077}What do you see to see there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.37,0:15:37.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:935372,937958}Just awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.46,0:15:44.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:943464,944923}What's up, Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.30,0:15:50.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:948302,950220}The road has disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.68,0:15:55.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:951680,955267}The sea was sunk by the tidal wave…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.26,0:15:56.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:955267,956477}Hey…!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.47,0:15:58.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:956477,958228}Someone help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.22,0:16:00.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:958228,960898}The road has disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.98,0:16:04.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:962983,964693}They can't hear us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.94,0:16:08.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:965944,968405}This is not the time to search for treasure…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.94,0:16:11.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:968947,971909}We have to think about the way back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.49,0:16:14.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:972493,974536}Colin, can you swim?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.53,0:16:16.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:974536,976872}I can't swim…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.87,0:16:19.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:977873,979708}Me neither…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.00,0:16:23.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:981001,983795}In the meantime, John and\NSandy will notice that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.25,0:16:28.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:984254,988467}If they don't notice quickly, the ship\Nbound for Australia will be departed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.46,0:16:32.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:989468,992054}Me too, maybe I can't…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.05,0:16:33.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:992054,993805}Anyway, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.39,0:16:39.18,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:995390,999186}I don't mind not going to Australia…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.18,0:16:39.81,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:999186,999811}Chris…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.18,0:16:45.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1001188,1005108}The treasure was a memory of my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.52,0:16:47.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1005526,1007069}A memory?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.06,0:16:50.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1007069,1010113}My mother died last month.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.61,0:16:56.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1012616,1016537}My father remembered when\Nthey lived in the same house.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.53,0:16:59.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1016537,1019790}He therefore decided to live\Nin a foreign country to build a new life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.74,0:17:04.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1020749,1024086}I really want to live here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.08,0:17:06.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1024086,1026421}But I can't say that to my father…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.42,0:17:07.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1026421,1027047}I see…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.75,0:17:10.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1027756,1030801}So before leaving England
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.80,0:17:14.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1030801,1034805}I decided to look for my mother's memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.80,0:17:21.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1034805,1041436}When I was small, my father, my mother\Nand me came here to play a treasure game.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.43,0:17:23.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1041436,1043313}It was fun…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.31,0:17:26.81,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1043313,1046817}The map is from my mom\Nthat's why I care about it a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.40,0:17:30.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1048402,1050821}After all this…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.82,0:17:33.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1050821,1053323}I haven't found it…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.78,0:17:38.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1056785,1058745}Let's go and find it… Chris!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.28,0:17:39.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1059288,1059997}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.99,0:17:42.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1059997,1062708}You can't leave without your precious treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.70,0:17:45.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1062708,1065627}But we have to think about the return!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.62,0:17:47.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1065627,1067838}I-I'll find a solution!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.83,0:17:50.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1067838,1070465}So let 's go, Chris!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.59,0:17:52.38,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1071592,1072384}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.77,0:18:05.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1083770,1085606}North West! North West!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.60,0:18:07.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1085606,1087399}Chris, is it that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.39,0:18:08.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1087399,1088900}Yeah, no mistake on that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.57,0:18:15.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1094573,1095532}It's there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.53,0:18:17.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1095532,1097409}It was buried under that tree!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.86,0:18:19.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1097868,1099286}You're not wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.28,0:18:21.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1099286,1101246}When I was little I was here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.24,0:18:22.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1101246,1102914}- We've found it!\N- Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.25,0:18:28.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1105250,1108629}My mother planted the seed,\Nit has already grown!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.62,0:18:30.00,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1108629,1110005}And now let's dig!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.00,0:18:31.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1110005,1111256}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.85,0:18:46.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1124853,1126938}Ah! Beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.39,0:18:49.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1127397,1129608}My mother wanted to see\Nhim with someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.65,0:18:52.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1130651,1132653}It seems to have something written!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.65,0:18:54.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1132653,1134446}Oh really!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.86,0:18:56.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1134863,1136615}Dear Chris,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.61,0:19:01.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1136615,1141536}When you read this you should\Nbe grown up and be a good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.00,0:19:10.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1149002,1150170}Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.96,0:19:18.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1155967,1158637}I have to go to Australia!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.63,0:19:20.34,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1158637,1160347}If my father doesn't see me,\NI'll be in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.60,0:19:24.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1163600,1164351}Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.26,0:19:27.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1166269,1167396}Let's go back…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.81,0:19:35.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1172818,1175445}Even if it slips from me, I won't sink.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.44,0:19:37.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1175445,1177239}I will swim and call for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.23,0:19:39.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1177239,1179116}At this time, just wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.53,0:19:41.45,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1179533,1181451}I'll go with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.45,0:19:44.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1181451,1184037}It's not good to go both of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.03,0:19:46.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1184037,1186123}So we won't be able to help each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.12,0:19:47.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1186123,1187082}But…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.08,0:19:49.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1187082,1189084}I'll be fine, leave the rest to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.45,0:19:50.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1189459,1190585}Colin…!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.17,0:19:55.21,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1193171,1195215}Do your best, Colin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.59,0:19:57.21,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1195590,1197217}Faster! Faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.09,0:19:58.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1198093,1198802}Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.17,0:20:03.18,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1199177,1203181}If delayed, the ship bound\Nfor Australia will be departed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.18,0:20:05.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1203181,1205308}Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.51,0:20:07.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1205517,1207436}Stop it, Colin Jones!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.43,0:20:09.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1207436,1209146}Go back to the ground quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.14,0:20:11.18,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1209146,1211189}Turn! Turn around!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.18,0:20:12.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1211189,1212441}We will help you now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.40,0:20:14.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1213400,1214192}We survived…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.35,0:20:17.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1214359,1217195}xxx
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.32,0:20:22.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1218321,1222200}The ship bound for Australia\Nwill leave immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.20,0:20:23.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1222200,1223410}Don't be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.41,0:20:24.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1223410,1224703}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.45,0:20:27.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1225454,1227330}She seems to have no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.33,0:20:28.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1227330,1228874}You have to say farewell now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.87,0:20:29.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1228874,1229708}Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.66,0:20:33.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1231668,1233628}Chris, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.62,0:20:35.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1233628,1235130}Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.13,0:20:36.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1235130,1236798}You go to Australia…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.79,0:20:41.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1236798,1241470}Thanks to you, Colin, I found\Nthe most precious thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.47,0:20:42.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1241470,1242596}Thank you, Colin!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.88,0:20:44.34,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1243889,1244347}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.05,0:20:50.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1248059,1250270}Thank you, Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.48,0:20:54.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1252481,1254691}Goodbye, John! Sandy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.69,0:20:55.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1254691,1255776}Goodbye, Chris!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.77,0:20:57.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1255776,1257027}Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.48,0:21:00.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1258487,1260530}Goodbye… Colin!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.53,0:21:06.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1264534,1266244}Chris! Chris!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.28,0:21:09.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1266286,1269748}Colin, I'll never forget\Nwhat happened this day!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.95,0:21:12.50,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1269956,1272501}Me too! Me too!\NI'll never forget!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.50,0:21:15.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1272501,1275045}Goodbye! Goodbye, Chris!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.54,0:21:17.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1275545,1277798}Goodbye… Chris…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.34,0:21:20.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1279341,1280801}Chris has already left.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.80,0:21:24.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1280801,1284971}Listen, did you find the treasure?\NWhat was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.97,0:21:25.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1284971,1285847}I'm sorry, John…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.76,0:21:28.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1286765,1288683}It's a secret!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.68,0:21:30.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1288683,1290435}It's only for two people!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.23,0:21:34.18,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1293230,1294189}Colin…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.52,0:21:36.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1294523,1296149}Isn't it, Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.14,0:21:38.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1296149,1298193}And now everyone, get ready to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.73,0:21:40.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1298735,1300403}Woe to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.32,0:21:45.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1301321,1305408}{\i1}We have to go back because\Nit's waiting for us now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.40,0:21:47.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1305408,1307702}What?
Comment: 0,0:21:56.83,0:21:56.83,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:1316837,1316837}Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.50,0:22:02.34,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1319506,1322342}{\i1}Has the influenza epidemic\Nspread in the village?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.34,0:22:04.71,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1322342,1324719}{\i1}Even my father got sick and stayed at home!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.71,0:22:06.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1324719,1326096}{\i1}And daily visit,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.09,0:22:08.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1326096,1328515}{\i1}are very tiring for my mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.51,0:22:10.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1328515,1330100}{\i1}Is she okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.68,0:22:13.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1330684,1333603}{\i1}Next episode:\N"It's Serious! My Mother Collapsed".
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.06,0:22:15.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1334062,1335647}{\i1}Be sure to watch!
